  <?dbhtml filename="hicolor-icon-theme.html" ?>

  <title>hicolor-icon-theme-&hicolor-icon-theme-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      The hicolor-icon-theme package contains a default fallback theme for
      implementations of the icon theme specification.
    </para>

